Class QuartileFilter

java.lang.Object
  PotentialClassIgnorer
      durbin.weka.QuartileFilter

public class QuartileFilter
extends PotentialClassIgnorer

An attribute filter that converts a numeric attribute into a two-state nominal attribute split into either upper/lower quartiles or above/below median.
